er-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;\">✓ Rs 750 credit per referral</li>\n        <li style=\"padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;\">✓ Advanced analytics dashboard</li>\n        <li style=\"padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;\">✓ Rs 2,000 monthly bonus</li>\n        <li style=\"padding: 8px 0;\">✓ Priority support</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background: white; border: 2px solid #e5e5e5; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; text-align: center;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #222; margin-bottom: 12px;\">Platinum Referrer</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; color: #2563eb; margin-bottom: 16px;\">16+ Referrals</div>\n      <ul style=\"list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #555; text-align: left;\">\n        <li style=\"padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;\">✓ Rs 1,000 credit per referral</li>\n        <li style=\"padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;\">✓ Full suite of tools & analytics</li>\n        <li style=\"padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;\">✓ Rs 5,000 monthly bonus</li>\n        <li style=\"padding: 8px 0;\">✓ Dedicated account manager</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>"
